<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>JEHOVAJERE</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Jesuh nih a zultu hna sinah, daihnak hnangamnak kan pek lai, Lungrethei le vansang au in um ti hlah uh,
 Pathian fapa Jesuh zum u law nan herh mi vialte an pek lai
 Kan nunnak ah khua khangtu Jehovajere.

[C1]
   Jehovah Sama kan sinah um, Jehovah Salom, kan hna ngamnak Jehovah Zere nih khua a khan, Jehovah Sabot in kan tei cang
   Halleluijah a min lianngan, chin ko seh.

[V2]
 A zumtu vialte bia a kan kamh, nan herh mi vialte a akn pek lai
 Nan zumh ah cun Pathian sunparnak nan hmuh lai
 Zumhnak in thlacam mi vialte nih, Khuaruahhar
 Thil lianngan an hmu, Kan nunnak ah khua khangtu Jehovajere.

[V3]
 Abraham nih Pathian biakam bang, Isak raithawinak a tuah tikah Jehovah Zere a sinak kha, a langhter i,
 Tuufano te raithawinak caah, an herh mi vialte a pek hna
 Kan nunnak ah khua khangtu Jehovajere.</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
</song>